OL,3,CBoy killed in Derby bus crash was
OL,4,C'sweet child that was full of life'
OL,6,FThe family of schoolboy who was killed
OL,7,Fwhen his bicycle was involved in a
OL,8,Fcrash with a bus and car in Derby have
OL,9,Fdescribed him as "caring,
OL,10,Fcompassionate, impulsive and
OL,11,Finquisitive".
OL,13,FSeth Fulton, aged 11, suffered serious
OL,14,Finjuries in the incident in Chaddesden
OL,15,Fon Friday, April 17, and died in
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,18,FHis family have now released a photo
OL,19,Fand paid tribute to Seth, who they say
OL,20,Fwas happiest when out in nature on an
OL,21,Fadventure.
