OL,3,CBoy killed in Derby bus crash was
OL,4,C'sweet child that was full of life'
OL,6,FSeth's mum and dad said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "He was a lovely colourful
OL,8,Flad, independent and cheeky. He had a
OL,9,Flust for life, loved wildlife and was
OL,10,Fadventurous.
OL,12,F"He was caring and compassionate,
OL,13,Fimpulsive and inquisitive. He had a
OL,14,Fthirst for knowledge, was fearless,
OL,15,Fvery sociable and would speak to
OL,16,Fanyone. He was free thinking and care
OL,17,Ffree.
OL,19,F"He absolutely loved skateboarding and
OL,20,FBMX riding. He was so very funny with
OL,21,Fhis silly jokes and dancing.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
