OL,3,CBoy killed in Derby bus crash was
OL,4,C'sweet child that was full of life'
OL,6,F"He was passionate about anything he
OL,7,Fput his mind to ` he had the best
OL,8,Fpersonality. Everyone who came into
OL,9,Fcontact with Seth will never forget
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,F"He loved his friends as much as they
OL,13,Fall loved him. He was a sweet child
OL,14,Fthat was full of life. He was a so
OL,15,Fvery loved son, brother, grandson and
OL,16,Fnephew."
OL,18,FDerbyshire police has launched an
OL,19,Finvestigation into the crash on
OL,20,FNottingham Road and has appealed for
OL,21,Fany dashcam footage to be handed in.
